{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KreatureKind is an approachable and wholesome Card Battler/Deck Builder, where you debate monsters to save magic!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Build your team from the seven playable characters (pick Luca if you like a sad emo boy, Riley for killer dance moves). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each has their own strengths and weaknesses, which need to be balanced to win debates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020740/extras/Steam_GifFrame_5.gif?t=1732652001\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Easy to learn, hard to master</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even if you're new to this kind of game, you'll figure it out.  <br>(It's okay, Quinn isn't much of a gamer either)  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Played every card battler on the market? These monsters will still give you a run for your money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020740/extras/Steam_Portrait_GifFrame_4.gif?t=1732652001\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Use your cards to debate monsters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you don't convince them to join your cause, magic will disappear forever. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No pressure! :3  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020740/extras/Steam_Portrait_GifFrame_5.gif?t=1732652001\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover, unlock, upgrade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features seven playable characters with different focuses, numerous plushies that make them better in discussions, and a whole bunch of cards to build your strategies around. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_par